1. *Sedeo* sam kod kuće celo veče. (I sat at home all evening.)
2. Oni su *sedeli* na klupi u parku. (They were sitting on a bench in the park.)
3. Kada sam došao, ona je već *sedela* za stolom. (When I arrived, she was already sitting at the table.)
4. *Sedela* sam pored prozora i gledala napolje. (I sat by the window and looked outside.)
5. Možete *sesti* na stolicu pored mene. (You can sit on the chair next to me.)
6. On je *seo* u automobil i krenuo. (He sat in the car and drove off.)
7. Nisam *seo* za računar danima. (I haven't sat at the computer for days.)
8. *Sedi* ravno! (Sit up straight!)
9. *Sedni* ovde pored mene. (Sit here next to me.)
10. *Sedela bih* ovde satima da gledam zalazak sunca. (I would sit here for hours to watch the sunset.)